'''伊丽莎白·方达儿·诺伊费尔德'''（{{lang-en|'''Elizabeth Fondal Neufeld'''}}，{{bd|1928年|9月27日|catIdx=Elizabeth Fondal Neufeld}}），[[美国|美国]]遗传学家，其研究集中在人体[[代谢性疾病|代谢性疾病]]的遗传原因而著名<ref>{{cite book | language = en |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=wwu7HmSv4jkC&q=%22Neufeld,+Elizabeth%22+1928&dq=%22Neufeld,+Elizabeth%22+1928&hl=en&sa=X&ei=OtiWUYOqG4WpiQLPt4HYBg&ved=0CFkQ6AEwCA|title=Contemporary Authors| volume= 161| editor=Terrie M. Rooney|publisher=Gale / Cengage Learning|year= 1998|isbn= 9780787619947}}</ref>，並因此獲得[[沃爾夫獎|沃爾夫獎]]、[[拉斯克臨床醫學研究獎|拉斯克臨床醫學研究獎]]、[[美國國家科學獎章|美國國家科學獎章]]等獎項。

==生平==
諾伊費爾德有俄國猶太人血統，1940年時為了逃避納粹迫害，與其俄籍猶太家屬從巴黎移民至美國；<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | last1 = Hirschhorn | first1 = K. | year = 1983 | title = The William Allan Memorial Award. Presented to Elizabeth F. Neufeld, Ph. D., at the annual meeting of the American Society of Human Genetics Detroit, September 29-October 2, 1982 | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-human-genetics_1983-11_35_6/page/1077| journal = American Journal of Human Genetics | volume = 35 | issue = 6| pages = 1077–80 | pmid = 6417998 | pmc = 1685992 }}</ref>在紐約安置後，諾伊費爾德先後就讀{{le|亨特学院校园学校|Hunter College High School}}與[[皇后學院|皇后學院]]，並在1948年從皇后學院獲得科學學士。畢業後，諾伊費爾德於[[緬因州|緬因州]]{{le|巴爾港|Bar Harbor, Maine}}{{le|傑克遜實驗室|Jackson Laboratory}}擔任研究助理，研究[[小鼠屬|小鼠]]的[[血液學|血液系統疾病]]。諾伊費爾德後來就讀[[加州大學柏克萊分校|加州大學柏克萊分校]]，研究[[核苷酸|核苷酸]]和複合式碳水化合物，並於1956年獲得博士學位。<ref>{{cite web | language = en | title = Elizabeth F. Neufeld - Department of Biological Chemistry, UCLA | url = http://www.biolchem.ucla.edu/people/faculty/elizabeth-f-neufeld | publisher = Department of Biological Chemistry, UCLA | accessdate = 2016-07-17 | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190609025749/http://www.biolchem.ucla.edu/people/faculty/elizabeth-f-neufeld | archive-date = 2019-06-09 }}</ref>

諾伊費爾德的研究後來受到廣泛地認同，由於她對[[溶小體儲積症|溶小體儲積症]]的論證及其基礎理論等應用科學研究，做出極大的貢獻，先後獲得[[沃爾夫獎|沃爾夫獎]]<ref name="Wolf">{{cite web | language = en | title = Wolf Prize Recipients in Medicine | url = https://www.jewishvirtuallibrary.org/jsource/Society_&_Culture/wolfmed.html | publisher = Jewishvirtual Library | accessdate = 2016-07-17 | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190509192211/https://www.jewishvirtuallibrary.org/the-wolf-prize | archive-date = 2019-05-09 }}</ref>、[[拉斯克臨床醫學研究獎|拉斯克臨床醫學研究獎]]，並在1994年獲得[[美國國家科學獎章|美國國家科學獎章]]。<ref name="Allan">{{cite web |language=en |title=The President's National Medal of Science: Recipient Details - Elizabeth F. Neufeld |url=http://nsf.gov/od/nms/recip_details.cfm?recip_id=253 |publisher=National Science Foundation. |accessdate=2015-03-13 |deadurl=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630011444/https://www.nsf.gov/od/nms/recip_details.jsp?recip_id=253 |archive-date=2019-06-30 }}</ref>

諾伊費爾德自1984年起擔任[[加州大學洛杉磯分校|加州大學洛杉磯分校]]生物化學系系主任，並在2004年退休。<ref>{{cite web|language=en|title=Elizabeth F. Neufeld, Ph.D.|url=http://fdb5.ctrl.ucla.edu/biological-chemistry/institution/personnel?personnel_id=45290|publisher=computing technologies research laboratory|accessdate=2015-03-13|deadurl=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190624212909/https://fdb5.ctrl.ucla.edu/biological-chemistry/institution/personnel?personnel_id=45290|archive-date=2019-06-24}}</ref>

== 獎項與榮耀 ==
1975年，諾伊費爾德獲得{{le|迪克森獎|Dickson Prize}}醫學獎。<ref>{{cite web |language=en |title=Karl Deisseroth, MD, PhD - Dickson Prize in Medicine |url=http://www.dicksonprize.pitt.edu/recipients/2015-deisseroth.php |publisher=University of Pittsburgh |accessdate=2015-03-13 |deadurl=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190815125953/http://www.dicksonprize.pitt.edu/recipients/2015-deisseroth.php |archive-date=2019-08-15 }}</ref>

1982年，諾伊費爾德因研究[[溶小體儲積症|溶小體儲積症]]引起的症狀，獲得[[拉斯克臨床醫學研究獎|拉斯克臨床醫學研究獎]]。<ref>{{cite web |language=en |title=Lasker Awards |url=https://www.nih.gov/about-nih/what-we-do/nih-almanac/lasker-awards |publisher=National Institutes of Health (NIH) |accessdate=2015-03-13 |deadurl=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200108234059/https://www.nih.gov/about-nih/what-we-do/nih-almanac/lasker-awards |archive-date=2020-01-08 }}</ref>同年，諾伊費爾德獲得{{le|威廉艾倫特別貢獻獎|William Allan Award}}。<ref name="Allan"/>

1984年，諾伊費爾德因研究[[黏多醣貯積症|黏多醣貯積症]]，獲得[[克瑞森獎章|克瑞森獎章]]。<ref>{{cite web |language=en |title=Elliott Cresson Medal |url=http://www.ebooklibrary.org/articles/elliott_cresson_medal |publisher=World eBook Library - eBooks |accessdate=2015-03-13 |deadurl=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190222145339/http://www.ebooklibrary.org/articles/elliott_cresson_medal |archive-date=2019-02-22 }}</ref>

1988年，諾伊費爾德與{{link-en|昂利·厄爾|Henri G. Hers}}因對[[溶小體儲積症|溶小體儲積症]]研究，共同獲得[[沃爾夫醫學獎|沃爾夫醫學獎]]。<ref name="Wolf"/>

1994年，諾伊費爾德獲得[[美國國家科學獎章|美國國家科學獎章]]生物學獎。<ref>{{cite web |language=en |title=Awards & Honors |url=http://www.ucla.edu/about/awards-and-honors/faculty-honors |publisher=UCLA |accessdate=2015-03-13 |deadurl=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190716192136/http://www.ucla.edu/about/awards-and-honors/faculty-honors |archive-date=2019-07-16 }}</ref>

